OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774339478
OL,3,CMan, 32, arrested after death of woman
OL,4,Cin Bristol
OL,6,FA 32-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder following the
OL,8,Fdeath of a woman in Bristol.
OL,10,FAmbulance crews were called to a
OL,11,Fproperty in Sussex Place, St Pauls, at
OL,12,Faround 8.40pm last night (Friday 20th
OL,13,FMarch), where a woman was found dead.
OL,15,FAvon and Somerset Police arrested a
OL,16,Fman on suspicion of murder at the
OL,17,Fscene, and he remains in custody.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
