CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774339478
OL,3,CMan, 32, arrested after death of woman
OL,4,Cin Bristol
OL,6,FA formal identification process of the
OL,7,Fdeceased woman has not yet been
OL,8,Fcompleted, but officers believe she
OL,9,Fwas in her thirties. Her family have
OL,10,Fbeen informed.
OL,12,FAn investigation has been launched by
OL,13,Four Major Crime Investigation Team
OL,14,F(MCIT) and enquiries continue to be
OL,15,Fcarried out at the scene.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
