FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774339478
OL,3,CMan, 32, arrested after death of woman
OL,4,Cin Bristol
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Neil Meade, from
OL,7,FMCIT, said: "A thorough investigation
OL,8,Fwill be carried out, and our thoughts
OL,9,Fare with the family of the woman at
OL,10,Fwhat will be an incredibly difficult
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"Specially trained family liaison
OL,14,Fofficers will continue to support the
OL,15,Ffamily. An investigation is now
OL,16,Funderway as we work to establish the
OL,17,Ffull circumstances of her death, and
OL,18,Fthis will mean there will be a
OL,19,Fsignificant police presence in the
OL,20,Farea over the coming days.
OL,26,@oD@MOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774339478
OL,3,CMan, 32, arrested after death of woman
OL,4,Cin Bristol
OL,6,F"We know this news will come as a
OL,7,Fshock to the community and people will
OL,8,Fbe concerned, but we are not looking
OL,9,Ffor anybody else in connection to this
OL,10,Fdeath, at this time.
OL,12,F"Anybody with concerns is advised to
OL,13,Fspeak to neighbourhood officers, who
OL,14,Fwill be carrying out extra patrols in
OL,15,Fthe area."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@JO]
